      "text": [
        "4657 - وَ فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ: \"لَمْ يَرْتَدَّ إِلَيْهِ طَرْفُهُ حَتَّى يُعْقِبَهُ اَللَّهُ إِيمَاناً يَجِدُ طَعْمَهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4657 - And in another narration: \"His gaze will not return to him until Allah (swt) grants him faith, the sweetness of which he will experience.\""
        ]
      }
    }
